interesting points: The photographs were taken at night or in low-light conditions., Four distinct objects were photographed, each having unique shapes and brightness., A silhouette resembling a key is visible in one of the photographs., One of the images contains a handwritten numeral '6' which adds to the mystery., The images depict various bright objects against dark backgrounds.
sighted object: elongated bright object, teardrop-like shape, crescent-shaped object, dot-like object
witness description: No witnesses are mentioned in the report.
